        <Parent_String>Phoenicopteriformes (order) [300310640], Aves (class) [300266506], Vertebrata (subphylum) [300265720], Chordata (phylum) [300266513], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family containing around three genera and five living species of tall, long-necked, long-legged, pink-colored, large-winged, wading birds with thick downturned bills. The birds were previously classified with the the long-legged Ciconiiformes based on certain physical characteristics, although now they are generally placed in their own family.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>科名，科下約含有三個屬與五個現存物種，體型高大而頸長、腿長、羽毛為粉紅色、翅膀巨大的涉禽類，具有厚而向下彎曲的喙。此鳥類之前由於其特定生理特徵而被分類為長腿的鸛形目，但現在通常歸於自屬的一科。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Familie bestaande uit ongeveer drie geslachten en vijf levende soorten grote rozekleurige waadvogels met lange nek, lange poten, grote vleugels met dikke omlaag gerichte snavels. De vogels werden voorheen op basis van bepaalde lichaamskenmerken geclassificeerd bij de langpotige Ciconiiformes, maar worden nu meestal tot een aparte familie gerekend.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
